nd does fear produce? </div><div class="t me4 x26 h27 yf50 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t m32e x4e h27 yf50 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Of what does the presence of fear give evidence? </div><div class="t m79b x15 h27 ye38 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">III. </div><div class="t m30e x61 h87 ye38 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A </div><div class="t m14ab x5f h27 ye38 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Proof of Discipleship. Verse 19-21, </div><div class="t me4 x26 h27 ye03 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t m377 x4e h27 ye03 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why do believers love God? </div><div class="t me4 x26 h27 yb8f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m537 x4e h27 y154c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What charge is made against him who professes </div><div class="t m571 x15 h27 y12df ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">love to God but hates his brother? </div><div class="t ma8e x92 h30 yd85 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Pray ye therefore the Lord of the harvest that He will send </div><div class="t m425 x6 h30 yf0e ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">forth laborers </div><div class="t md31 x77 h16 yf0e ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">into </div><div class="t m114f x2a h30 ye15 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His harvest.&quot; </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
